review: Crazy how good this thing is. Only suggestion from me would be a replay button for when I want to listen to a tone while sleeping. Other than that, this is the perfect app for meditation and focus.
sentence: Only suggestion from me would be a replay button for when I want to listen to a tone while sleeping.
